    <briefdescription>
<para>Grid information for time and frequency axes associated with FFT arrays. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This class describes the time and frequency grids with steps <formula id="172">$ h $</formula> and <formula id="183">$ d\omega $</formula> and length <formula id="184">$ N_{ft} $</formula> used in <computeroutput><ref refid="classness2_1_1fft__array" kindref="compound">fft_array</ref></computeroutput> and <computeroutput><ref refid="classness2_1_1herm__matrix__ness" kindref="compound">herm_matrix_ness</ref></computeroutput>.</para>
<para>Given:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para><computeroutput><ref refid="classness2_1_1grid__info_a3718e03f5f27d955fbb85aafff80fe2e_1a3718e03f5f27d955fbb85aafff80fe2e" kindref="member">h_</ref></computeroutput>: time step,</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><computeroutput><ref refid="classness2_1_1grid__info_a7897d0d1ee6b8206d66338b10520d6ac_1a7897d0d1ee6b8206d66338b10520d6ac" kindref="member">Nft_</ref></computeroutput>: total FFT grid points,</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><formula id="185">$ {\tt dw\_} = \frac{2\pi}{{\tt Nft\_} \cdot {\tt h\_}} $</formula>: frequency step. </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
